title: Russians boasted that just 1% of fake social profiles are caught, leak shows
description: An analysis of Russia’s effectiveness at boosting propaganda on social media platforms is part of a trove of documents recently leaked on the chat app Discord.

title: See the tests of SpaceX’s Starship prototypes that ended in fireballs
description: Elon Musk's SpaceX is expected to attempt to launch its fully stacked Starship as soon as this week. Take a look back at the rocket's test flights.

title: SpaceX’s launch of Starship could remake space exploration
description: Powered by a staggering 33 first-stage engines, Starship and its booster are expected to have nearly twice the thrust of NASA's SLS moon rocket.
